{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1681-03_346"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Madrigal sur le gros Lot gagné par le Roy]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", mars 1681 [tome 3], p. 346-348."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je croyois vous envoyer la Liste des noms de tous ceux que la Fortune a favorisez à la Loterie du Roy ; mais beaucoup de Boëtes qui ne sont point revenuës de la Campagne, estant cause qu’il reste encor plusieurs Lots à délivrer, je suis obligé de remettre cet Article. En vous l’envoyant, je vous feray part de quelque chose sur ce sujet qui vous surprendra agreablement. Voicy cependant un Madrigal de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " Guyonnet de Vertron, sur ce que le Roy ayant gagné le gros Lot, le doit remettre à une seconde Loterie en faveur de ceux qui n’ont rien eu. Ce Lot en fera plusieurs, & la Loterie sera tirée apres Pasques. Je vous parleray de toutes les deux dans le mesme temps."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ouy, les Siecles suivans auront peine à le croire ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "La Justice, l’Honneur, la Sagesse, la Gloire,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Accompagnent le Roy,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Tout fléchit sous sa Loy,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Ciel le favorise, & mesme la Fortune,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour le suivre par tout, luy paroist importunes"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Son grand cœur, & ses yeux, ont les mesmes objets,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il voudroit que son sort tombast sur ses Sujets ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "chi